  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eI may have fallen victim to my love for touring cars at \u003ca href=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/tag/2024-essen-motor-show/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethis year’s Essen Motor Show\u003c/a\u003e, paying little attention to anything else. Sorry, not sorry.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOkay, that’s not entirely true. This is the second spotlight on historic racers from the show. However, \u003ca href=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-golden-age-of-touring-cars-at-essen-motor-show-2024/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eunlike the legendary machines featured in my previous post\u003c/a\u003e, these aren’t the iconic names of the Group A era.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174703/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-10.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174703/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-10-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-10\" data-attachment-id=\"658758\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174703/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-10.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-10/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174703/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-10-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174831/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-28-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-28\" data-attachment-id=\"658776\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174831/EMS-