e touring car world from a simpler time – when Group 2 regulations ruled, and from 1971 a European Touring Car Championship class dedicated to cars under 1,300cc existed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174838/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-29.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174838/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-29-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-29\" data-attachment-id=\"658777\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174838/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-29.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-29/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174838/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-29-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174756/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-21-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-21\" data-attachment-id=\"658769\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174756/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-21.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-21/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174756/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-21-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174807/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-23-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-23\" data-attachment-id=\"658771\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174807/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-23.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-23/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174807/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-23-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174716/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-13-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-13\" data-attachment-id=\"658761\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174716/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-13.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-13/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174716/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-13-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor those of you who measure in freedom units, that’s just a mighty 79 cubic inches.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174639/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-4-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-4\" data-attachment-id=\"658752\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174639/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-4.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-4/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174639/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-4-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne car missing from this lineup is the stunning Alfa Romeo GT Junior, the first winner of the 1,300 division championship. What you see here, instead, is a fascinating mix from various decades, countries, and drivetrain configurations.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174800/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-22-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-22\" data-attachment-id=\"658770\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174800/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-22.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-22/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174800/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-22-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174812/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-24-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-24\" data-attachment-id=\"658772\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174812/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-24.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-24/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174812/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-24-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174855/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits\" data-attachment-id=\"658780\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174855/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174855/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe NSU TT is one of my favourite shapes from the ’60s. With its rear-engined, air-cooled, rear-wheel-drive layout, it’s a quirky little car. NSU was an interesting brand, absorbed into Auto Union, which later became modern-day Audi. And yes, it served as the inspiration for the now-iconic Audi TT, both in name and design philosophy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174746/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-19-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-19\" data-attachment-id=\"658767\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174746/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-19.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-19/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174746/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-19-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174731/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-16-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-16\" data-attachment-id=\"658764\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174731/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-16.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-16/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174731/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-16-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eItaly and France have long been masters of small-car engineering, and the beautiful Fiat 128 Coupé was a competitive contender when it debuted in the 1972 series. Then there’s this Renault 5, which surprised me. Aside from the wild R5 Turbo II in rallying, I had no idea the Renault 5 had raced in any major circuit-based series.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174707/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-11.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174707/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-11-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-11\" data-attachment-id=\"658759\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174707/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-11.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-11/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174707/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-11-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd that’s the beauty of \u003ca href=\"https://www.1300etc.de/en/\"\u003ethe 1300 European Touring Car Challenge (1300 ETC) championship\u003c/a\u003e today. It’s a fairly open series, allowing any sub-1,300cc car that follows the regulations up to the 1981 FIA Appendix J rules to enter.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174651/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-7.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174651/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-7-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-7\" data-attachment-id=\"658755\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174651/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-7.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-7/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174651/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-7-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThat’s why this Mk1 VW Polo is in the mix. In Europe, these little hatchbacks are well-regarded as Berg Cup hill climb machines, but after watching a few 1300 ETC races, I can assure you the competition is as fierce as ever, no matter the age of the cars or their original purpose.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174845/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-30-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-30\" data-attachment-id=\"658778\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174845/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-30.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-30/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174845/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-30-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174712/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-12-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-12\" data-attachment-id=\"658760\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174712/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-12.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-12/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174712/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-12-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174654/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-8-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-8\" data-attachment-id=\"658756\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174654/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-8.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-8/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174654/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-8-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174632/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-3-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-3\" data-attachment-id=\"658751\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174632/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-3.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-3/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174632/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-3-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174659/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-9-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-9\" data-attachment-id=\"658757\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174659/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-9.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-9/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174659/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-9-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174751/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-20-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-20\" data-attachment-id=\"658768\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174751/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-20.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-20/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174751/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-20-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174721/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-14-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-14\" data-attachment-id=\"658762\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174721/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-14.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-14/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174721/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-14-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174727/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-15-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"EMS 24 MC SH 1300 Edits-15\" data-attachment-id=\"658763\" data-go-fullscreen=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174727/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-15.jpg\" data-can-print=\"true\" data-attachment-url=\"https://www.speedhunters.com/2024/12/the-1300-etc-racers-of-essen-motor-show-2024/ems-24-mc-sh-1300-edits-15/\" data-src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/speedhunters-wp-production/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/13174727/EMS-24-MC-SH-1300-Edits-15-1200x800.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreserving historic race series is important, but it can be prohibitively expensive. These small but mighty racers offer a relatively affordable entry point into the world of historic touring cars – and they deserve to be celebrated.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI wonder how much a Mk1 Ford Escort 1300 is going for these days…\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMario Christou\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\nInstagram: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mcwpn\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emcwpn\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mariochristou.world\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emariochristou.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mariochristou.world/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emariochristou.world\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\t\n\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ch3\u003eOFFICIAL SPEEDHUNTERS SUPPLIERS\u003c/h3\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
